## AbstractMap.get() method

Returns the value associated to the `key`<!-- -->, or `undefined` if there is none.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
get(key: K): V | undefined;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  key | K | The key of the element to return from the map. |

<b>Returns:</b>

V \| undefined
